commit.message: Bug fixes, UI improvements, addition of SplitViewController support for the displayModeButtonItem, DELETED QRCodeReader CocoaPod due to general incompatibility

AutoLayout optimization for iPhone X, MKCamera bug fixes, Asset additions, implemented Mail sending (MessagesUI) from SettingsViewController, ensured that downloaded profile pictures save to UserDefaults

Implemented functionality for creating, saving, and retrieving TPPass instances, complete with imageData. Updated WatchKit app with the correct key-value pairs to prevent app crashing. Changed startDate and endDate properties of TPPass to be of type NSDate.

Completely redesigned SettingsViewController to dynamically add LocationNameCells and other cells using delegation. Updated FirebaseStorage class. Added support for changing the account profile picture.

Fixed issues with Core Data and invalid Firebase key names for the TPLocationTile chunks with decimal latitude and longitude. Now, a latitude of SXX.NNNNNNNNNN converts to SXXNN in the key. Fixed FirebaseStorage directory references.

Worked with Core Data Models and Firebase Object graphs, extensions, LocationTypePicker, and firebase implementation of completely creating a new location. Also implemented loading locations on MapViewController. Also added stopNonKeywords.
Continued working on Location Management, updated all objects with the TP class prefix and updated Core Data Model with correct Firebase properties. Added Plus Button icon.
Added redesigned app icons throughout the system as well as fixed bugs on NewLocationViewController and PinSelectionViewController. Added information to DatabaseManager
Marker
Linked NewLocationViewController to PinSelectionViewController and implemented all Pin passing and management.

Completed most of the delegation in SplitViewController as well as worked with PassesViewController to properly change the detail controller when cells are selected and when rows are deleted. Changed PassDetailViewController's row heights to be UITableViewAutomaticDimension.

Configured database management functions and nearly completed the SplitViewController / PassDetailViewController / GuestsInfoViewController trifecta. FINALLY fixed issue of ContactView background disappearing. Worked with Firebase.

Primarily worked with Accounts.swift to ensure that important user data is always available, and ensured that the login process includes data retrieval and saving. Added more FirebaseObjects to support with fast data retrieval later. Added LocationManager. Added tap recognizer to LocationCell to zoom to specific locations.
Completely re-layed out the MapViewController using a ManagedViewController instead of a UITableViewController. Added shadows to LocationCells and fixed proportion layouts with their subviews.
Added new plus button icon

Completed animations in LoginViewController using CGAffineTransform(translationX:y:). Removed excess code in NewAccountViewController. Fixed issues in enhancement classes and a crash bug in CEViewController with alert styles. Began GeolocationManager.validateGeofenceMonitoring()
Updated True Pass Database Model pages document, added explicit enumerations for some TPObject values, added first launch detection and presentation of info controller, added new icon
Added dynamic styling of alert actions to CEViewController, worked with Accounts.swift, added email verification check before login. Added logout functionality to SettingsVC.

Configured first functions for uploading and retrieving images from FirebaseStorage. Worked with many methods in LoginViewController, NewAccountViewController, and viewDidLoad in SettingsViewController
Updated all CocoaPods and added FirebaseStorage to support the storing of images.

Almost completely configured NewAccountViewController (added photo picking ability and profile picture requirement), fixed an issue in WCSessionManager where the pass image wasn't being sent, created and configured CPPhotoPicker and added its functionality into NewAccountViewController, implemented CPTextFieldManager in LoginViewController, added comments to CPContactsManager

Added dynamic Quick Actions, added CEViewController to manage alert presentations, added CPContactsManager to manage contactsUI choosing, edited many view classes and fixed extensions, changed the scan quick action icon, fixed login view controller lag delay on startup, implemented most of the new account view controller.

Finished adding all location icons and location scenes; added view controllers that walkthrough True Pass and information about it, added a forgotpassword view controller, configured managedViewController to listen for keyboard notifications, fixed an issue in MapViewController with screen orientation decisions, fixed 3DQuick action for updated True Passes Page View Controller

Completely configured CPTextFieldManager, changed the NewPassViewController class and its storyboard ViewController to reflect this, and created the AboutTruePassViewController and DevelopmentViewController

Added LocationDetailViewController and AdministrationViewController, configured UIPageViewController for multiple TruePasses, refactored some methods from C to UIAlert, configured segues and their identifiers, began GeoLocationManager and CPTextFieldManager, edited many views and fixed bugs.
Added NewAffiliationViewController and began to work on rounding SettingsViewController UITableViewCells
Updated entitlements for iOS App and WatchKit app and also updated package structure and file locations for WatchKitExtension
Modified package structure by putting each swift class into its proper sub folder
Worked on view controller layouts for the check in pass controller and new location controller
Added Database Model pages document
